Subject: [PATCH] media: cadence: csi2rx: Configure DPHY using link freq
Git-commit: a91d06f46bf725f97d2bf344294c54bc57686889
References: jsc#PED-10837
Patch-mainline: v6.7-rc1

Some platforms like TI's J721E can have the CSI2RX paired with an
external DPHY. Use the generic PHY framework to configure the DPHY with
the correct link frequency.

Signed-off-by: Pratyush Yadav <p.yadav@ti.com>
Tested-by: Julien Massot <julien.massot@collabora.com>
